Start
/ Integration cut 1 — runtime spine: int literal + decimal literal → math.add
/ promotes to Decimal → 4.5. The .pr-shape claims (which kinds get stamped on
/ which params) are pinned in C# BuilderKindStampingTests; variable.set's
/ polymorphic Value gets no kind, typed kind-bearing params do.
- set %x% = 1
- set %z% = 3.5
- math.add A=%x% B=%z%, write to %b%
- assert %b% equals 4.5
